  ('social-worker-moex-02201', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列對零基預算（zero-based budgeting）的描述，何者有誤？', '["不囿於上年度或以前年度預算數字的高低，重新審視其業務活動，決定其優先順序", "是將每年的預算從「零」的基準開始", "每一個組織的預算編列得將過去抹掉，每一年根據所需的財務狀況重新做調整", "在於「累積」，藉由成本效益分析，選出合乎成本又有助於目標達成的方案"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02202', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下對工作分析（job analysis）的描述，何者有誤？', '["指有系統蒐集組織中各項工作職責與員工所應具備的基本條件內容", "是分辨各工作職務對於組織價值相對的貢獻度與重要性", "工作分析所蒐集的資料包括：工作資料、行為資料與技能資料", "工作分析結果可做為工作說明書、招募甄選、人力規劃時的參考資料或依據之一"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02203', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '持「管理系統（managed system）」理論觀點的學者認為，非營利機構董事會不會具有下列那項功能？', '["監督行政管理成效", "確保必要資源（包括財源與人力資源）的輸入", "提名適當的候選人加入董事會，建構有效的治理體系", "甄選與解聘基層員工"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02204', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下對社會行銷（social marketing）內涵的陳述，何者有誤？', '["是一種為了解決募款不足的策略之一", "社會行銷僅適合由營利組織來推行或運用", "社會行銷的目標在於促進個人、團體或社會整體之福祉", "銷售行為改變的過程"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02205', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '為了確保人力需求的適當性，執行人力資源規劃（human resources planning）是必要的工作。下列何者與 人力資源規劃無關？', '["工作分析", "工作說明書", "組織人力服務手冊", "制定事業策略及分析"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02206', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下有關非營利組織資訊揭露（information disclosure）的說明，何者有誤？', '["資訊揭露的目的是要解決因資訊不對稱（asymmetric information）所引致的代理問題（agency problem）", "資訊揭露是非營利組織形成責信（accountability）的主要途徑之一", "在資訊不對稱的關係中，代理人無法直接觀察委託人的行動", "對資訊揭露的激勵與監督措施，可降低資訊不對稱所引致的道德風險"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02207', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在規劃組織員工訓練過程（training process）或訓練計畫時，不會考慮下列那個步驟？', '["組織使命與價值分析", "訓練目標訂定", "訓練課程設計與執行", "評估訓練方案是否達成既定目標"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02208', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會服務領域常用的品質要素，「能夠以一致和穩定的方式提供服務，即使不同服務對象與時間，仍極 少變動。」指的是下列那一種要素？', '["保證性", "才能、技術和知識", "可靠性", "公平性"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02209', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '方案評估之類型中，「檢驗提供服務與使用資源之間的比值（ratio）」是那一種方案評估之類型？', '["效力評估", "整體表現之適切性", "成本效率評估", "成本功效評估"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02210', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「某機構正在等候進住的人數」之陳述，是屬於下列何種需求評量的類型？', '["規範性需求（normative need）", "相對性需求（relative need）", "感受性需求（perceived need）", "表達性需求（expressed need）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a074978a4189", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a21ae17ed63d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "107", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
